summary: This is a save of a pretty redhead nord.
descriptionHtml:
This is a save of a pretty redhead nord. There are two save files here. One is at lvl 1 just as soon as you get to Riverwood. No quests done. and with a bit of loot ready to sell. The second is at lvl 29 with some basic quests done.
Just thought i\'d share. Lemme know what ya\'ll think.
